{
  "stem": "365.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I say to him, again, chief, if you give me a pencil and paper, I think I can find the mistake what I made.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I sit down, and I first draw myself a diagram-- how the wires should be for the double switch-- the three wires, the two plus, the one minus, I think.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I open up the junction box, climb up, and look at it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It doesn't take me five minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found which wires are crossed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I untangle it, put it together, switch on the work-- hurry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That guy, the chief grabs-- no, told me before when I thought.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, you find the mistake before the engineer gets back, and you have a whole loaf of bread from me tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I finished, and I switch on the light, and it works individually, he grabs himself by the hat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he says straight to the other Germans, now those are the Jews!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Their ingenuity and their-- think what they-- how they comprehend things is beyond me, he says.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, now when he's fired from here or transferred, he will apply for the job as a electrician.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And believe me, he will do the job, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, well, Ziegler, you earned the loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you'll get it tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you keep your mouth shut when the engineer comes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And let me do the talking to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To make a long story short, the engineer comes back after lunch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, don't worry, gentlemen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We will find the mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everything is fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he goes over to him and says, Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Engineer-- it was-- it's customary in Europe, you know, a guy that has any degree, any title, to call by that title.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
